> ===
. * Merge IMF non-fuel commodity shocks (AR(1) innovations on dln_imf)
. *============================================================================
> ===
. preserve

. import delimited "../data/clean/imf_shocks.csv", clear varnames(1)
(encoding automatically selected: ISO-8859-1)
(3 vars, 337 obs)

